03:15.028 --> 03:16.613
- I'm fine. I'm fine.

03:18.115 --> 03:20.450
I can't find my special necklace.

03:20.534 --> 03:23.370
The one that I had custom-made
with "RBG"--

03:23.453 --> 03:24.913
Ruth Bader Ginsburg.

03:24.997 --> 03:26.456
- It's okay. It's okay.
- Yeah.

03:26.540 --> 03:27.958
She's my favorite Supreme Court justice.

03:28.041 --> 03:30.878
I mean, I love her dissenting opinions.

03:30.961 --> 03:34.298
